== Births == * [[承和 (日本)|Shōwa]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[835]] {{ill|June 5|ja|6月5日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 5|qq=}}) – Heira Hiro, one of the four sons of Hira Takamochi of the Kantō Taira clan (died [[928]]). * [[応保]] 2nd year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1162]] {{ill|June 20|ja|6月20日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 20|qq=}}) – Benchō, a monk of the Jōdo-shū (died [[1238]]).
== Deaths == * [[Emperor Jomei]] 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[635]] {{ill|May 27|ja|5月27日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 27|qq=}}) – Emperor Jomei, the first emperor of the Tang dynasty of Japan (also known as Li Yuan, the founding emperor of the Tang in China; born [[566]]). * {{ill|Tenpyō-hōji|ja|天平宝字|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Tenpyō-hōji|qq=}} 7th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[763]] {{ill|June 21|ja|6月21日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/June 21|qq=}}) – the great monk {{ill|Ganjin|ja|鑑真|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Ganjin|qq=}}, a prominent Chinese Buddhist monk who founded the Japanese Ritsu school (born [[688]]). * [[Ōei]] 15th year ({{ill|Julian calendar|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|ja|ユリウス暦|1=Julian calendar|2=ja|3=ユリウス暦|4=zh|5=儒略曆|6=ru|7=Юлианский_календарь|8=de|9=Julianischer_Kalender|10=es|11=Calendario juliano|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|13=User:Immanuelle/Julian calendar|qq=}} [[1408]] {{ill|May 31|ja|5月31日|qq=|qq=draft|12=simple|13=User:Immanuelle/May 31|qq=}}) – Ashikaga Yoshimitsu, the 3rd shōgun of the Ashikaga Shogunate (born [[1358]]). * {{ill|Tenshō|ja|天正|1=T